<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">我今年的目標，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是和<tag a="110" b="4" />
多聊聊天喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />看來馬上就能
達成目標了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的新年初夢會夢見什麼呢？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果能夢到和<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
一起吃<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />的夢就好了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />我今天晚上<delay8 />
可以把<tag a="110" b="4" />的照片<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />放在枕頭下睡覺嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說到新年，就會想到新春試筆對吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 />一旦真的要下筆了，<delay8 />
又會很猶豫要寫些什麼呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果<delay20 />我每年都還是<delay8 />
寫了「新年初曙」四個字，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在正值新年，<delay8 />
所以我嘗試做了年節料理。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我是照著媽媽教的方法去做，<delay20 />
但感覺成品就是不太一樣呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來我得在下次做年節料理前，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />先踏實地練習了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天是一年的尾聲，<delay8 />
所以有不少事情要忙，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在順利迎來新年，<delay8 />總算讓我鬆了口氣呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天我決定休息一天，<delay8 />
不做打掃和洗衣服這些家事，<delay20 />
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好好享受新年假期喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
</msbt>